{"type":"message","id":"4aea4eae","parentId":"55b2ef81","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:45:29.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, committed. Now let me summarize what I've done for Zach.","thinkingSignature":"5af54b0d130e7523b8204577def27a6c6b14df9bef32b14e71384027d2f76cd4"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's what I set up:\n\n**Context Management System** (`CONTEXT.md`):\n- **4-tier hierarchy**: Always-in-context (tiny) → Session memory → Project context → Long-term memory\n- **Summarization trigger** at ~60% context usage\n- **Session continuity protocol**: Always write session summary before end\n\n**Active Projects Tracker** (`memory/active-projects.md`):\n- Priority queue with Component Crate flagged as 🔴 CRITICAL\n- Status tracking for all known projects\n- Session log noting the previous session was reset (context lost)\n\n**Updated Session Startup** (`AGENTS.md`):\n- Now reads `CONTEXT.md` and `memory/active-projects.md` on every fresh start\n\nThe system is now in place. One thing I can't solve retroactively: whatever you were working on before the `/reset` is gone — the session transcript wasn't preserved. If Component Crate had active work, want to catch me up?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6874,"output":217,"cacheRead":11966,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19057,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774122323248}}
