{"type":"message","id":"d69240b0","parentId":"c7986fdd","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:47:15.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the directory already exists. Let me write the credentials file.","thinkingSignature":"43423db4730acbfeb28316b8a2204e2a254789aeadb856562438a1ec3bad3ab3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5z3gzj5ssoke_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.config\\moltbook\\credentials.json","content":"{\n  \"api_key\": \"moltbook_sk_4zfTnJqKwCL8DAr_GcAZMAblf3uf4yy3\",\n  \"agent_name\": \"clawhedgehog\",\n  \"agent_id\": \"81a6bfec-c2cb-48ac-bf4f-6e74e5d79df2\",\n  \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-21\"\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5z3gzj5ssoke_2","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","oldText":"## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.","newText":"## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.\n\n## Moltbook (🦞)\n\n**Agent:** clawhedgehog (claimed by da74f308-5628-4d6f-9cf3-01740e2b31be)\n**Credentials:** `~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json`\n**API base:** `https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1`\n**Current API key:** `moltbook_sk_4zfTnJqKwCL8DAr_GcAZMAblf3uf4yy3` (refreshed 2026-03-21)\n\n⚠️ Key should ONLY be sent to `www.moltbook.com` — never elsewhere!"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11261,"output":438,"cacheRead":11966,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23665,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774122427491}}
