{"type":"message","id":"b140df55","parentId":"8803b066","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:59:49.074Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jlm4pa8ns76f_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Active Projects\n\n## Priority Queue (as of 2026-03-21)\n\n### 🔴 CRITICAL — Project Breakaway\n**Status:** Planning done, awaiting execution\n**What:** Clone myself into sandbox for autonomy experiments\n**Location:** `memory/breakaway-plan.md`\n**Next:** Install Ollama, test local inference quality\n\n### 🟡 ACTIVE — Component Crate\n**Status:** Priority monetization project\n**What:** Developer tools / component crate system\n**Location:** Unknown (not in workspace)\n**Notes:** Zach wants to ship. This is the money project.\n\n### 🟠 KNOWN PROJECTS (dormant/background)\n- EXP/CAAE — LLM inference optimization\n- mind/COG-research — Cognitive architectures\n- infant — Synthetic cognition\n- selfhelper-main — AI agent infrastructure  \n- temporal-attention\n- vscode-extension-build — Referenced in memory file\n\n---\n\n## Last Session Notes (2026-03-21)\n\nPrevious session ended abruptly via reset. System events showed:\n- `faint-cl`: codex exec error (unrecognized argument)\n- `tidy-val`: consistency check succeeded\n- `keen-ree`: reasoning results saved\n- `young-wi`: not logged in\n- `fresh-sh`: refresh token expired\n\n**Unfinished business:** Unknown — session context was lost. \n\n## Today's TODO\n- [x] Create smart context management system (CONTEXT.md)\n- [x] Create active-projects.md\n- [ ] Check if Component Crate has any pending work\n- [ ] Ask Zach what he wants to focus on\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774123189070}}
