{"type":"message","id":"6d238612","parentId":"73f8de05","timestamp":"2026-03-21T20:00:20.030Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the Telegram logs:\n- The bot is `@BotShoppeBot` - this is a different bot than what Zach might be expecting\n- There's a pairing request from `Ton0Fun` at 15:00 (3:00 PM)\n- The bot is running in polling mode and seems to be sending/receiving messages\n\nThe issue might be:\n1. Zach is talking to a different bot\n2. The pairing/allowlist is blocking messages\n3. Zach needs to DM the right bot (@BotShoppeBot)\n\nLet me check the config to see what bot is set up.","thinkingSignature":"5d462a4f06abe92ee4bded9e305cafd48cb10a7b28f1c1224705b9725f3515ac"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cp7fdswfoci5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat \"$env:USERPROFILE/.openclaw/openclaw.json\" | ConvertFrom-Json | Select-Object -ExpandProperty channels | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27531,"output":186,"cacheRead":11966,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39683,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774123214211}}
